<plot>Eric Leiser displays his boundless creativity in this collectible shorts collection; A stunning compilation of works presented with a mixture of live action, stop motion animation, puppetry and pixilation techniques, produced between 2001 and 2006. From a vast array of obscure images, wild locations and masterful set creations, Leiser presents a stark and comprehensive world with unrelenting vision and an original voice. Original music by Jeffrey Leiser</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?165160</url></doc>
